description: Foodies of Washington D.C., watch out for Ada’s Kitchen on Wheels if you’re craving quality comfort cuisine made with love, soul, and care. Your taste buds will be quite thankful when you find all your favorite Southern hankerings on this mobile menu: Fresh hot fried chicken with the perfect amount of crisp, lip-smackin’ mac & cheese that’ll take you right back to your most scrumptious childhood memories, crunchy cool coleslaw, and that’s not even all. With over 250 years of recipes and tradition behind every dish, you can count on every bite to be absolutely delicious. Make your day the yummy way with a belly & soul-warming meal from Ada’s Kitchen on Wheels.
name: Ada's Kitchen on Wheels
